Package: mframe
Type: Package
Title: Data Frames with Metadata
Version: 0.0-1
Date: 2009-06-08
Author: Enrique Bengoechea <enrique.bengoechea@credit-suisse.com>,
Maintainer: Enrique Bengoechea <enrique.bengoechea@credit-suisse.com>
Description: 'mframe' is an S3 class that adds metadata to data frames.
    Metadata is modelled with S3 classes 'varMetadata' and 'dfMetadata'
    that accept user-defined per-variable metadata and also permit
    parameterization of data frame operations with type checking,
    validation, default values, or row keys.
Depends: R (>= 2.8.1), methods
Imports: ppTools
Suggests: svUnit
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
Collate: 'dfMetadata.R' 'generics.R' 'metadata.R' 'mframe.R'
    'mframe_subset.R' 'varMetadata.R' 'zzz.R'
